    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Double-strength glass that has one side ground to a frosted finish, thus transforming the clear glass to an obscure glass.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
